 was also able to put his opponent under pressure, as one should be really brave ot take on e2 - and it did not happen in the game: Svidler - Anand, chess24.com 2020.}) 12... Nde7 {The most natural square for the knight, consolidating both sides of the board.} (12... Nb6 13. Nc3 Nc4 14. Qe2 {is already great for White.}) 13. Qc1 a5 14. a4 $5 Qb6 15. Ra3 $1 e5 16. Nc3 {White has a small edge here.} *

