Qc8 15. h4 {It's a pity we could not play Qa4-h4 here!} (15. Nc4 Na6 $132) (15. Kh2 a5 {Protecting the b4-knight to threaten ...Nxe5.} 16. Qb3 Be6 17. Nc4 Rd8 $132 {With ...a4 coming, Black has interesting compensation.}) 15... a5 $1 {Again, protecting the b4-knight to enable ...Nxe5.} (15... Bg4 $6 16. Bf4 Bxf3 17. Bxf3 Bxe5 18. Bh6 Bg7 19. Bxg7 Kxg7 20. Nc2 Qf5 $5 {A key move, otherwise White is simply better.} 21. Nxb4 Qxf3 22. Nxc6 Qxc6 23. Qxc6 bxc6 24. Rd7 {And Black will anyway very much suffer in this rook endgame.}) 16. Qb3 Be6 17. Nc4 Rd8 18. Bf4 Rxd1+ 19. Rxd1 a4 20. Qc3 Nxa2 21. Qc2 Nab4 22. Qe2 {Black is quite passive and his position definitely unpleasant.} *

