and I would pick White, though Black should probably hold.}) 21. Ra1 Qc3 22. Rexa5 Bf5 23. Be3 Z0 ({After} 23... Nc4 24. Qb3 Qxb3 25. Nxb3 Nxa5 26. Nxa5 {Black hasn't made a draw yet, though with good play he should hold.}) *

