4 27. h4 {is highly unpleasant for Black.}) 24. Rxa5 Bc6 25. Rxc6 bxc6 26. Bxc6 {And the position is probably only equal, but Black had to find several precise moves. I haven't promoted 21. Qe4 for layout reasons, but this is definitely what I would try in a practical game!} *

