very passive position, where he’s also going to lose his extra pawn.} 14. Bb2 Nc6 15. f3 Re8 16. Rab1 f6 17. Bc3 {This is unpleasant for Black, who can't really move anything. Next is probably a4-a5: Dominguez Perez - Anand, Saint Louis 2018.} *

